@editcommunist

- @add5communistdissent: Add 5 Communist Dissent
- @100communistdissent: Maximum Communist Dissent
- @subtract5communistdissent: Remove 5 Communist Dissent
- @removecommunistdissent: Remove All Communist Dissent
- @add5communiststrength: Add 5 Communist Strength
- @100communiststrength: Maximum Communist Strength
- @subtract5communiststrength: Remove 5 Communist Strength
- @removecommuniststrength: Remove Communist Strength
- @returnsandbox: Return To Sandbox Menu

@add5communistdissent
go-to: editcommunist
on-arrival: {!
Q.communist_dissent += 5;
!}

Added 5 communist dissent.

@100communistdissent
go-to: editcommunist
on-arrival: {!
Q.communist_dissent = 100;
!}

Maximised communist dissent.

@subtract5communistdissent
go-to: editcommunist
on-arrival: {!
Q.communist_dissent -= 5;
!}

Reduced communist dissent by 5.

@removecommunistdissent
go-to: editcommunist
on-arrival: {!
Q.communist_dissent = 0;
!}

Removed all communist dissent.

@add5communiststrength
