@editironfront

- @formironfront: Form The Arditi del Popolo
- @raiseurgency: Raise Urgency Against The Fasci
- @lowerurgency: Lower Urgency Against The Fasci
- @returnsandbox: Return To Sandbox Menu

@formironfront
go-to: editironfront
view-if: arditi_formed = 0
on-arrival: {!
Q.arditi_formed = 1;
!}

Arditi del Popolo has been formed.

@raiseurgency
go-to: editironfront
on-arrival: {!
fasci_urgency += 1;
!}

Raised fasci urgency.

@lowerurgency
go-to: editironfront
on-arrival: {!
fasci_urgency -= 1;
!}

Lowered fasci urgency.

