@unbanabl
go-to: editparamilitary
view-if: abl_banned != 0
on-arrival: {!
Q.abl_banned = 0;
!}

Unbanned the Anti-Bolshevik Leagues.

@editreichswehr

- @raiserwstrength: Raise Army Strength By 25,000
- @lowerrwstrength: Lower Army Strength
- @raiserwloyalty: Raise Army Loyalty
- @lowerrwloyalty: Lower Army Loyalty
- @raiseipstrength: Raise Interior Police Strength By 25,000
- @loweripstrength: Lower Interior Police Strength
- @raiseiployalty: Raise Interior Police Loyalty
- @loweriployalty: Lower Interior Police Loyalty
- @returnsandbox: Return To Sandbox Menu

@raiserwstrength
go-to: editreichswehr
on-arrival: {!
Q.army_strength += 25;
!}

Raised army strength by 25,000.

@lowerrwstrength
go-to: editreichswehr
on-arrival: {!
Q.army_strength -= 25;
!}

Lowered army strength by 25,000.

@raiserwloyalty
go-to: editreichswehr
on-arrival: {!
Q.army_loyalty += 0.2;
!}

Raised army loyalty.

@lowerrwloyalty
go-to: editreichswehr
on-arrival: {!
Q.army_loyalty -= 0.2;
!}

Lowered army loyalty.

@raiseipstrength
go-to: editreichswehr
on-arrival: {!
Q.interior_police_strength += 25;
!}

Raised Interior Police strength by 25,000.

@loweripstrength
go-to: editreichswehr
on-arrival: {!
Q.interior_police_strength -= 25;
!}

Lowered Interior Police strength by 25,000.

@raiseiployalty
go-to: editreichswehr
on-arrival: {!
Q.interior_police_loyalty += 0.2;
!}

Raised Interior Police loyalty.

@loweriployalty
go-to: editreichswehr
on-arrival: {!
Q.interior_police_loyalty -= 0.2;
!}

Lowered Interior Police loyalty.

@editpartysupport

- @increasepsisupport: Raise PSI Support
- @decreasepsisupport: Lower PSI Support
- @increaseulsupport: Raise UL Support
- @decreaseulsupport: Lower UL Support
- @increaseldrsupport: Raise LDR Support
- @decreaseldrsupport: Lower LDR Support
- @increasedssupport: Raise DS Support
- @decreasedssupport: Lower DS Support
- @increaseppisupport: Raise PPI Support
- @decreaseppisupport: Lower PPI Support
- @increasepsrisupport: Raise PSRI Support
- @decreasepsrisupport: Lower PSRI Support
- @increasepnfsupport: Raise PNF Support
- @decreasepnfsupport: Lower PNF Support
- @increaseothersupport: Raise Other Support
- @decreaseothersupport: Lower Other Support
- @increasepcdisupport: Raise PCDI Support
- @decreasepcdisupport: Lower PCDI Support
- @increasepsusupport: Raise PSU Support
- @decreasepsusupport: Lower PSU Support
- @increaseprisupport: Raise PRI Support
- @decreaseprisupport: Lower PRI Support
- @increasepllsupport: Raise PLL Support
- @decreasepllsupport: Lower PLL Support
- @increasepcssupport: Raise PCS Support
- @decreasepcssupport: Lower PCS Support
- @returnsandbox: Return To Sandbox Menu

@increasepsisupport
go-to: editpartysupport
on-arrival: {!
Q.workers_psi += 10;
Q.middle_class_psi += 10;
Q.industrialists_psi += 10;
Q.rural_psi += 10;
Q.veterans_psi += 10;
Q.catholic_psi += 10;
Q.women_psi += 10;
!}

Raised support for PSI.


@decreasepsisupport
go-to: editpartysupport
on-arrival: {!
Q.workers_psi -= 10;
Q.middle_class_psi -= 10;
Q.industrialists_psi -= 10;
Q.rural_psi -= 10;
Q.veterans_psi -= 10;
Q.catholic_psi -= 10;
Q.women_psi -= 10;
!}

Lowered support for PSI.

